<main class="show-tour-container">
  <section>
  <%#= @tour.content.html_safe %>
    <div class="container mb-5">
      <h1 class="pt-4 pb-4 text-center"><%= @tour.title %></h1>
      <nav aria-label="breadcrumb">
        <ol class="d-flex list-inline">
          <li class="breadcrumb-item"><%= link_to "Home Page", root_path %></li>
          <li class="breadcrumb-item active" aria-current="page"><%= @tour.title %></li>
        </ol>
      </nav>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12">
          <%= render 'tours/partials/show_carousel' %>
          <%= render 'tours/partials/large_screen_img' %>
        </div>        
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="container">
        <h3 class="font-weight-bold">About this tour</h3>
        <div class="col-md-12 mt-3">
          <div class="d-flex icon-line-height mb-4">
            <div class="mr-2"><i class="h4 far fa-credit-card"></i></div>
            <div class="ml-2"><p>Free Cancellation</p><span class="text-muted">Cancel anytime for a full refund</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="d-flex icon-line-height mb-4">
            <div class="mr-2"><i class="h4 fas fa-virus"></i></div>
            <div class="ml-2"><p>COVID-19 Precautions</p><span class="text-muted">Special healt and safety measures apply.</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="d-flex icon-line-height mb-4">
            <div class="mr-2"><i class="h4 fas fa-skiing"></i></div>
            <div class="ml-2"><p>Skip the line</p><span class="text-muted">Skip the line through separate entrance.</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="d-flex icon-line-height mb-4">
            <div class="mr-2"><i class="h4 fas fa-headphones"></i></div>
            <div class="ml-2"><p>Audio Guide | Headphones</p><span class="text-muted">Spanish, Korean, Chinese, Italian, Russian, German, Hindi, Arabic.</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <hr>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="content">
          <h4 class="pt-2 pb-2"><%= @tour.title %></h4>
          <p>Early in the morning, you will be picked up from your hotel and you go to the airport. 
          And you fly to Izmir, meet with our tour guide when you land to the Izmir Airport. Ephesus, 
          was the second largest city in the Roman Empire over 250.000 people in the 1st BC. Ranking 
          only behind Rome it was the second largest city in the world? Ephesus was also a harbour city. 
          And, this giant city was built only with marbel. Did you know Ephesus had a largest amphitheater 
          in the ancient world over 25.000 seats. Also see Goddess Nike, Local pharmacy, Hadrian Gate, Library of Celcius 
          (the third largest library), Marbel Street and Harbour Street. Temple of Artemis or Artemision, also known as the 
          Temple of Diana, was a Greek Temple dedicated to the goddess Artemis. It was located in Ephesus and it was one of the seven wonders of the world. The House of Virgin Mary, is a place where according to the beliefs of many people Mary, the mother of Jesus, spent her last years of her life. She was supposed to arrive at Ephesus together with St. John and lived there in the years 37-45 CE until her Assumption or Dormition. After the tour, you will be transfered to the Izmir Airport. Fly back to Istanbul. When you arrive to Istanbul you will transfer back to your hotel.</p>
        </div>
        <%= render 'tours/partials/accordion' %>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="form-container p-4">
          <div class="my-3 text-center" id="form-total-price" data-price="<%= @tour.price %>">
            <h3>Total Price: <span id="display-total-price"><%= @tour.price %> USD</span></h3>
          </div>
          <%= render 'bookings/form', tour: @tour %>
        </div> 
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
<div class="container">
<h1>You may also like</h1>
  <div class="row">
    <% @tours.shuffle[0..1].each do |tour| %>
      <div class="card-trip col-lg-5 m-4 px-0 py-0">
        <%= cl_image_tag tour.photos[0].key, class: "card-tour-img", alt: "#{tour.title} Picture"  %>
        <div class="card-trip-infos">
          <div>
            <h2><%= link_to tour.title, tour_path(tour) %></h2>
            <p><%= tour.description %></p>
            <div class="d-flex icon">
              <i class="far fa-clock mt-2 mr-3"> <span><%= tour.duration %></span></i><br>
              <i class="fas fa-running mt-2 mr-3"> <span>Skip the line</span></i><br>
              <i class="fas fa-user-friends mt-2 mr-3"> <span><%= tour.group_size %></span></i>
            </div>
          </div>
          <h2>$ <%= tour.price %></h2>
        </div>
      </div>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="container mt-3 mb-3">
      <h3>Reviews from our clients</h3>
      <div id="reviews">
        <% if @tour.reviews.blank? %>
          <p class="mb-3">Be the first to leave a review for <strong><%= @tour.title %></strong></p>
        <% else %>
          <% @tour.reviews.each do |review| %>
            <p class="review-title p-3" id="review-<%= review.id %>"> <%= review.user.email %> <br> <% review.rating.times do %>
              <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
            <%end%> <br><%= review.title %></p>
            <p class="review-content p-3" id="review-<%= review.id %>"><%= review.content %></p>
          <% end %>
        <% end %>

        <% if @booking %>
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
              <%= simple_form_for([@booking, @review], remote: true) do |f| %>
                <strong><%= f.input :title, label: 'Highlight the experience' %></strong>
                <strong><%= f.input :content, label: 'Content' %></strong>
                <strong><%= f.input :rating, collection: (1..5).to_a, label: "Rate your experience" %></strong>
                <%= f.submit "Send Your Review", class: "btn btn-success" %>
              <% end %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
